title: Famously Single
itunes:title: Famously Single
description:
WED 6/15 - Supermodel Jessica White stops by The Breakfast Club to talk about her new show on E! "Famously Single" and why a woman of her stature has a problem finding a man. Donkey of the Day goes to a pastor who celebrated the Orlando tragedy. His church should be "Famously Empty".
